  "title": "Assistant Clinic Manager (Specialist Clinic) | Novena - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Assistant Clinic Manager</strong></u><br /><br />Working day: 5.5 days work week<br />Working Hour: Mon to Fri (9.00am – 5pm) | Sat (9.00am – 1:00pm)<br />Salary range: $3,000 - $4,000<br />Location: Mt. E Novena</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in the clinic’s day to day operations and functions.</li><li>Assist the Medical Director in the assigned clinic.</li><li>Responsible for all aspects of customer service including but not limited to cashiering, appointment booking, and answering customer enquiries.</li><li>Responsible for all matters pertaining to insurance, Medisave, and Letter of Guarantee(s).</li><li>Liaise with customers, vendors, suppliers, and local regulatory bodies when required.</li><li>Assist in the renewal of government licenses including but not limited to Clinic License, Fire, Insurance, and HSA.</li><li>Other duties assigned by your reporting officer as required.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>1-2 years Clinic Supervisor/Manager experience</li></ul><p><br /><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
